  <div class="container">
    <h1>Soling Stone Work</h1>
    <p>
      ðŸª¨ <strong>Soling Stone Work:</strong><br>
      Soling stone is the process of laying hard, durable stones closely packed over the ground surface to create a solid base. It is commonly used in road foundations, flooring of industrial areas, and below concrete slabs to improve stability and drainage. Khushi Construction ensures proper compaction and alignment for long-lasting results.
    </p>

    <h3>Applications:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Base for roads and pavements</li>
      <li>Under foundations and flooring</li>
      <li>Parking areas and industrial sheds</li>
      <li>Drainage improvement layers</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Benefits:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Strong and stable foundation base</li>
      <li>Improves drainage and reduces waterlogging</li>
      <li>Prevents settling and cracks in concrete</li>
      <li>Cost-effective and durable</li>
    </ul>

